{"tid":632013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港本土作家) 藍橘子: 「中國」電影和電視劇將超越「香港」","createTime":"2018-04-17T04:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T17:00:05.000Z","uid":134071,"like":11,"dislike":117,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"09f1c26180aa53069718d782cdcfee65453fd24c","tid":632013,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/BlueGodG/posts/1684693041645082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBlueGodG%2Fposts%2F1684693041645082&d=Dbc4MV86%2FLTMa%2BN%2BR%2BEI%2Bp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d644522a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/BlueGodG/posts/1684693041645082</a><br />\n<br />\n藍橘子<br />\n4月15日 17:12 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n其實很怕，中國電影、電視劇、漫畫、小說創作&hellip;終有一日會進步，然後超越香港。<br />\n　<br />\n可能１年、５年、１０年&hellip;（有些中國漫畫小說其實幾好睇）<br />\n　<br />\n但以香港人的個性，會以「不看」來蒙蔽現實。覺得大陸拍的是狗屎，不屑一看，固步自封，永遠沒進步。<br />\n　<br />\n眼看香港現時部分創作，很想抄襲韓國風，卻只抄了個皮毛&hellip;<br />\n　<br />\n皮毛就是普遍人眼中的「韓國明星只係整容、跳啲簡單舞、硬改電子音、歌詞重覆啫～都唔知紅乜&hellip;」<br />\n　<br />\n於是，出現很多簡單舞、硬改電子音、歌詞重覆的歌&hellip;柒到打冷震！<br />\n　<br />\n外國的抄不來，韓國又抄不像，永遠只看表面，而不是吸收學習再超越&hellip;"},{"pid":"4c061ca394d0972cbf485aed0cacb93cedae906d","tid":632013,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7e2f233bc5030d43592b68f6f91434cc551a43","tid":632013,"uid":41508,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:20:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b855ad7deead44771db35602fab62dcd0c8e48a","tid":632013,"uid":33668,"like":54,"dislike":4,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:20:47.000Z","msg":"作為作家竟然推崇&quot;抄&quot;呢個文化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫佢做香港本土作家真係失禮咗佢<br />\n明明個MINDSET咁「中國」"},{"pid":"09cd9ef7fa19f7884de2a51abcf6df944c6c1fdd","tid":632013,"uid":132302,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"