<br />\n但又無好深入接受下<br />\n<br />\n我地一味笑人地，但人地都有高質野出到嚟<br />\n但好矛盾<br />\n我都係佢筆下嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n因為我真係提唔起勁去接觸韓國文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f949a529c365c2da876025a429d027d158f75b7","tid":632013,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"啲咁嘅垃圾文筆都夠膽以作家自居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af54243c824250622a9c8bba35acb42977aed276","tid":632013,"uid":174403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:10:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上帝啲故 高登唔係好受歡迎嘅咩？<br />\n不過過左咁多年，連登應該無乜人識<br />\n<br />\n佢唔只有講韓國<br />\n印度電影都有講過<br />\n<br />\n我覺得有樣野講得幾好嘅<br />\n就係我地香港人一味話人差<br />\n但又無好深入<span style=\"color: red;\">了解</span>下<br />\n<br />\n我地一味笑人地，但人地都有高質野出到嚟<br />\n但好矛盾<br />\n我都係佢筆下嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n因為我真係提唔起勁去接觸韓國文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2e511992e4a98c4b88bb13ec055d32c507d3d010","tid":632013,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efc4f916e48b1acfdf0c3d1850508e700f39fd6c","tid":632013,"uid":33668,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"e2e457c51c8b8650416f5231fef5c4465d86f3f4","tid":632013,"uid":90863,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:25:57.000Z","msg":"邏輯幾混亂<br />\n寫返愛情小說啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:30:11.000Z","msg":"啱啱地但佢有好多都因為偽本土身份 想暗讚大陸又唔想畫出腸<br />\n又話香港學得唔似  言下之意 即係讚大陸學得好 但又唔可以畫大陸抄 奶到咁<br />\n然後想香港參考大陸<br />\n<br />\nLOGIC就係 香港應該學大陸定學大陸參考嘅方法定直接參考日韓美<br />\n<br />\n媽我好亂呀!!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"我心諗要抄參都直接搵美日韓啦 <br />\n可能實際想吹奏大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm